Summary: Taking random pictures and caught something on digital
divs: Sighting DetailsI was taking random pictures of the surroundings I was in when I had numerous sightings about a month ago. I seemed to have 'caught' something. I don't know what it is, but it sure appears as though it could be something other than a conventional aircraft. Here is a picture. There may be other 'anamolous objects as well.
